{"tid":2439610,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[佐敦名店喎]究竟係邊間X龍咖喱連支援路宿者既嘢都偷?","createTime":"2021-03-09T11:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T15:03:20.000Z","uid":56701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"717028d11e335403817658af0382b1bb2682157a","tid":2439610,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:17:23.000Z","msg":"首先呢..今次好快咁引用閪吱之前去試食果兩條片先...喺呢度要多謝佢,光頭佬你今次做到嘢呀! <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8YLOCNDj8oI&amp;ab_channel=MIHK.tv_Youtube%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8YLOCNDj8oI%26ab_channel%3DMIHK.tv_Youtube%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%258F%25B0&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=4463922a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8YLOCNDj8oI&amp;ab_channel=MIHK.tv_Youtube%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7f0O3FAZNqA&amp;ab_channel=MIHK.tv_Youtube%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7f0O3FAZNqA%26ab_channel%3DMIHK.tv_Youtube%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%258F%25B0&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=a928fff2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7f0O3FAZNqA&amp;ab_channel=MIHK.tv_Youtube%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後要再貼返點解我會注意到呢單嘢...係因為面書有人講...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AHMED.HONGKONG/posts/10159170755364820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAHMED.HONGKONG%2Fposts%2F10159170755364820&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=7f0194aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AHMED.HONGKONG/posts/10159170755364820</a><br />\n<br />\n但係以我所知兩間係唔同老闆,但我就從未食過...為免搞錯左,我睇左光頭佬食果兩條片...<br />\n<br />\n發現有兩個人身影最似面書控訴果間係响另一間啊字頭咖喱...<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">因為光頭佬食第二間發現廚房位係有個人好似面書所拍到個眼鏡男人...而有個比較肥既女士仲要係坐光頭佬後面...<br />\n<br />\n如果你去面書睇完佢個CCTV會發現四眼男人己先後幾次去偷人地支援路宿者既藍櫃...而最後灰色果段更拍到果個肥女人....</span></span>"},{"pid":"ea8137d967b24d159fa068f8a4aba96f9dbe6156","tid":2439610,"uid":88491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:26:49.000Z","msg":"唔洗估<br />\n佐敦亞龍咖哩個老細鬼鬼鼠鼠偷露宿者食物<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2408259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2408259</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"61710c74d89d75fbfe1f877a518e057a075771a3","tid":2439610,"uid":308618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:33:58.000Z","msg":"兩間舖老細都係仆街嚟。<br />\n<br />\n亞龍老細就偷露宿者物資。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿龍老細就起亞龍老細飛腳另起爐灶。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d644a1049aa5766af0c18a90a3cc58961e8ce5f7","tid":2439610,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"61710c74d89d75fbfe1f877a518e057a075771a3","tid":2439610,"uid":308618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:33:58.000Z","msg":"兩間舖老細都係仆街嚟。<br />\n<br />\n亞龍老細就偷露宿者物資。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿龍老細就起亞龍老細飛腳另起爐灶。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:43:03.000Z","msg":"起飛腳有幾仆街？即係成世寄人籬下打份工先叫好仔？"},{"pid":"f209b06f93361c5b9fbc8f4c4ce763320c142f4d","tid":2439610,"uid":308618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d644a1049aa5766af0c18a90a3cc58961e8ce5f7","tid":2439610,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"61710c74d89d75fbfe1f877a518e057a075771a3","tid":2439610,"uid":308618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:33:58.000Z","msg":"兩間舖老細都係仆街嚟。<br />\n<br />\n亞龍老細就偷露宿者物資。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿龍老細就起亞龍老細飛腳另起爐灶。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk